@vars f=SUPPORTED,m=SKIP_DIRS
estimateTokens(text:string)→Math.ceil|estimate token count from char length (÷4)
walkJSFiles(dir:string)→readdirSync,statSync,SKIP_DIRS.has|walk dir for .js/.mjs files, skip vendor/node_modules
